id: pmc-ysps
title: Release pm-changelog 0.1.0 as a production-ready pm package
description: "Govern the full release-readiness effort for pm-changelog, including package metadata, repository hygiene, secret-history review, GitHub configuration, changelog generation, and independent installation testing."
type: Epic
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[3]: governance,production,release
