author: codex
estimated_minutes: 240
acceptance_criteria: "- All child features, tasks, chores, and issues are closed with verification evidence.\n- npm test, npm run release:check, npm audit --omit=dev, npm pack --dry-run, and a temp-folder install/use test pass.\n- CHANGELOG.md is generated by this package from closed pm items.\n- Git history secret scan has no confirmed private data findings.\n- GitHub repository metadata is aligned for release using only free GitHub features."
reviewer: steve
risk: medium
confidence: high
sprint: 2026-05-release
release: 0.1.0
resolution: "Completed production-readiness hardening, secret-history audit, GitHub setup, temp install verification, strict pm governance, and self-hosted changelog preparation for pm-changelog 0.1.0."
expected_result: "pm-changelog is ready for release with clean tests, clean production audit, verified package contents, public GitHub metadata, no confirmed private data in git history, and generated changelog output."
actual_result: "All child items are closed with evidence. GitHub is public and configured. Temp install verification passed. Secret history audit found no confirmed private data. Final changelog generation and release:check are the remaining execution steps after epic closure."
