close_reason: Release-readiness work is complete; all child items are closed and final changelog/release checks are ready to run.
body: "Scope:\n- Verify package metadata, license, CI, generated dist output, and npm package contents.\n- Verify the complete git history does not expose private credentials or private key material.\n- Verify the package installs and runs from a clean temporary project through the pm package manager and standalone CLI.\n- Ensure GitHub repository settings use only free features and match public package expectations.\n- Use pm-changelog itself to regenerate CHANGELOG.md from closed pm items before release."
